---
layout: layout/base.njk
permalink: false
metaRobots: "noindex, nofollow"
metaTitle: "SEO Audit Internal — Site Map"
metaDescription: "Página interna de auditoría SEO — listado de URLs con sus titles y meta descriptions. Excluida de indexación."
---
<div class="height-sm bg-light"></div>
<div class="container ptr-64 pbr-64">
  <h1 class="fluid-4-r mb-32">SEO Sitemap interno</h1>
  <p class="text-14-r mb-24" style="color:var(--c-gray);">Esta página tiene <code>noindex,nofollow</code> y está bloqueada en <code>robots.txt</code>. Solo para uso interno de auditoría.</p>

  <ul class="list-clear">
    {% for page in collections.all | sort(attribute='data.metaTitle') %}
      {% set robots = page.data.metaRobots or "" %}
      {% if page.data.metaTitle and "noindex" not in robots and page.url != "/site/" %}
        {% set t = page.data.metaTitle %}
        {% set d = page.data.metaDescription or "" %}
        {% set k = page.data.metaKeywords or "" %}
        {% set tlen = t.length %}
        {% set dlen = d.length %}
        <li class="mb-32" style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding-bottom:16px;">
          <a class="ttc" href="{{ page.url }}"><strong>{{ page.url }}</strong></a>
          <br><b>metaTitle ({{ tlen }} chars):</b>
            <span class="{% if tlen < 30 or tlen > 65 %}red-text{% endif %}">{{ t }}</span>
          <br><b>metaDescription ({{ dlen }} chars):</b>
            <span class="{% if dlen < 120 or dlen > 320 %}red-text{% endif %}">{{ d }}</span>
          <br><b>metaKeywords:</b> <span>{{ k }}</span>
          <br><b>metaRobots:</b> <span>{{ robots }}</span>
        </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>

<style>.red-text{color:#C0392B;font-weight:600;}</style>
